OL,5,Cman
OL,7,FMarcin Majerkiewicz, 42, who also has
OL,8,Fa tattoo of slasher-film character
OL,9,FJason from Friday The 13th, bludgeoned
OL,10,FStuart Everett with a hammer at the
OL,11,Fhouse they shared in Winton, Salford.
OL,13,FHe then used a hacksaw to dismember
OL,14,Fhis 67-year-old housemate and friend
OL,15,Fbefore taking the body parts in
OL,16,Fplastic bags on bus journeys across
OL,17,FSalford and north Manchester to dump
OL,18,Fthe evidence.
