OL,7,FThe Polish national later pretended to
OL,8,Fbe Mr Everett to throw friends and
OL,9,Ffamily off the trail, using his phone
OL,10,Fand bank cards, as well as sending a
OL,11,Fbirthday card in his name to his
OL,12,Fbrother, after his death.
OL,14,FMajerkiewicz, a dad-of-two with his
OL,15,FPolish ex-partner, denied
OL,16,Fresponsibility for the killing but
OL,17,Foffered no evidence in his defence and
OL,18,Fhis motive remains unclear.
