OL,7,FJurors convicted him of murder in
OL,8,Funder two hours of deliberations
OL,9,Ffollowing a three-week trial at
OL,10,FManchester Crown Court.
OL,12,FJailing him for a minimum of 34 years
OL,13,Fyears Mr Justice Cavanagh told
OL,14,FMajerkiewicz, who looked ahead with no
OL,15,Femotion, he had shown no remorse.
OL,17,FHe said: "You acted in an almost
OL,18,Funbelievably cold-blooded and macabre
OL,19,Fway, and showed complete disrespect
OL,20,Fand contempt for your friend's remains.
