OL,7,F"This denied dignity to Stuart Everett
OL,8,Feven in death, and greatly increased
OL,9,Fthe pain suffered by Stuart Everett's
OL,10,Ffamily when the murder came to light."
OL,12,FHe added: "Through the way in which
OL,13,Fyou behaved in the aftermath of Stuart
OL,14,FEverett's death showed an extremely
OL,15,Fdistasteful willingness and perhaps
OL,16,Feven enthusiasm to butcher his body."
OL,18,FHis brother Richard Ziemacki, in a
OL,19,Fvictim impact statement read to the
OL,20,Fcourt, said: "It's extremely difficult
OL,21,Fto put into words how much I miss him.
