OL,7,FBorn Roman Ziemacki in the UK, of
OL,8,FPolish parents, and originally from
OL,9,FDerby, he first met his killer while
OL,10,Fteaching English to recently arrived
OL,11,FPolish immigrants.
OL,13,FMr Everett, who had worked for both
OL,14,Fthe NHS and Department for Work and
OL,15,FPensions, was known as "Benny" to his
OL,16,Ffamily, was not married and had no
OL,17,Fchildren, and was a fan of "Rat Pack"
OL,18,Fsingers Dean Martin and Frank Sinatra.
OL,20,FHe also enjoyed gardening, cricket and
OL,21,Fa bet on horses.
