OL,14,Fof hours of CCTV, tracking the
OL,15,Fdefendant's movements, also
OL,16,Fdiscovering human remains at Linnyshaw
OL,17,FColliery Woods, Blackleach Reservoir,
OL,18,FWorsley Woods and Boggart Hole Clough.
